<h1>Welcome to Beaver Fest Managment System!</h1>

<p>This application allows you to manage all aspects of the festival logistics. Please select a category below to view, add, or edit entries.</p>

<ul>
    <li><a href="/bands"><strong>Manage Bands</strong></a> - View and add musical acts.</li>
    <li><a href="/venues"><strong>Manage Venues</strong></a> - Manage stages, booths, and their capacities.</li>
    <li><a href="/performances"><strong>Manage Performances</strong></a> - Schedule bands to specific venues and times.</li>
    <li><a href="/managers"><strong>Manage Managers</strong></a> - View staff managing the venues.</li>
    <li><a href="/sponsors"><strong>Manage Sponsors</strong></a> - View corporate sponsors and contributions.</li>
</ul>

